page.title: 15Lifestyles_David aged 8
page.content: I get up always at 7.00am. At 8.00 I go and have my bacon sandwich then I clean my teeth and I go to school and line up to go in. When we go in we usually do some number work together and have a story.First play is at 10.30am and I play FORTY_FORTY.It is a game_a person is IT and he counts to forty and the rest hide and save themselves and the last person can all. Lunch time is at 12.00. Afternoon school starts at 1.15pm.Then we usually do P.E. Last play is at 2.30pm,then at 3.35pm we go home. After tea I sit in front of the television and I go to bed at 9.00pm.
